fehd.ADR_EN: PORTION OF 1/F. AND 2/F., WYNDHAM MANSION, 32 WYNDHAM STREET, CENTRAL, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環雲咸街32號雲咸大廈一樓部份及二樓

result.adr_address: 32 Wyndham St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: The Flying Elk Hong Kong

reviews.text: This restaurant serves really tasty and beautifully presented Scandinavian style food in a relaxing ambiance. Really like this place which has always lived up to expectations each and every time. Feels so fresh and modern. The food is creative and interesting. Very friendly staff. Can highly recommend!
Nice crab roll for starter, fish and chips, good apple crumble. Fish was really nice quality buy too soft in my view but that one purpose I understood. Good coffee. Nice venue and good staff.
The Best Nordic Restaurant I ever been. Food was great! My favorite was Scallop. I am in love with their West Coast cocktails. Attentive Service and ambiance is fantastic. Try this out!
Great ambience and drinks, with friendly staff. This restaurant offers a unique dining experience. What’s not to like?

first time Flying Elk - very good experience - team
is friendly and helpful, food is delicious (tasting menu)  and wine/drinks selection is good enough. what i like is that even the place has many tables, it still makes you feel a special guest. thats not easy. liked it - will go back. 

not easy to find the entrance, so i posted a pic of the map. enjoy.
